name: Calor Rimax
description: Everyone who has lived or felt the warmth of the Caribbean has been sitting in a Rimax chair. Nothing like being in front of the sea eating a shrimp cocktail while the legs of the chair are buried in the sand. This chair is loaded with memories of my childhood and my adulthood. The heat and emotion made an object. If you have one of these, it's because you're one of mine.
